        "---\n",
        "## Step 4 — Map Job Titles → 22 Candidate Roles (Fuzzy Matching)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Problem found in EDA:**\n",
        "- Job titles are free text with 72,521 unique values\n",
        "- Candidate job_role has only 22 clean categories\n",
        "- Direct string match would fail (\"Senior Data Scientist II\" won't match \"Data Scientist\")\n",
        "\n",
        "**Fix:** Use RapidFuzz `token_sort_ratio` to find the closest of the 22 candidate roles for each job title. Store both the matched role and the confidence score.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Why needed for ranking:** The role match signal needs a comparable role label per job.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 8,
      "id": "4ea13b02",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "4ea13b02",
        "outputId": "f2af9d7b-b2f7-4a90-8037-3330f157c82c"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "22 candidate roles: ['Data Scientist', 'Frontend Developer', 'Backend Developer', 'Designer', 'Full Stack Python Developer', 'Finance', 'Game Developer', 'DevOps Engineer', 'Full Stack Java Developer', 'Blockchain Developer', 'Marketing', 'HR', 'C# Developer', 'PHP Developer', 'Mobile Developer', 'Cybersecurity Engineer', 'Software Project Manager', 'Video Game Designer', 'Data Analyst', 'Kubernetes Operations Engineer', 'Web Developer', 'AIML']\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "from rapidfuzz import process, fuzz\n",
        "\n",
        "JOB_ROLES = candidate_df['job_role'].unique().tolist()\n",
        "print(f\"22 candidate roles: {JOB_ROLES}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 9,
      "id": "aab68dc3",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "aab68dc3",
        "outputId": "4f6d6fad-4da5-4bef-bdb4-af143d0a9b83"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Sample fuzzy role mapping:\n",
            "                                                       title                    matched_role  role_score\n",
            "0                                      Marketing Coordinator                       Marketing      0.6000\n",
            "1                          Mental Health Therapist/Counselor  Kubernetes Operations Engineer      0.4127\n",
            "2                                Assitant Restaurant Manager        Software Project Manager      0.4706\n",
            "3   Senior Elder Law / Trusts and Estates Associate Attorney  Kubernetes Operations Engineer      0.3256\n",
            "4                                         Service Technician                 DevOps Engineer      0.3636\n",
            "5                   Economic Development and Planning Intern              Frontend Developer      0.5172\n",
            "6                                                   Producer        Software Project Manager      0.3125\n",
            "7                                          Building Engineer          Cybersecurity Engineer      0.5641\n",
            "8                                      Respiratory Therapist                  Data Scientist      0.4000\n",
            "9                                             Worship Leader                Mobile Developer      0.4000\n",
            "10                         Inside Customer Service Associate             Video Game Designer      0.3846\n",
            "11                                         Project Architect        Software Project Manager      0.4390\n",
            "12             Appalachian Highlands Women's Business Center  Kubernetes Operations Engineer      0.3733\n",
            "13                                       Structural Engineer  Kubernetes Operations Engineer      0.5306\n",
            "14                          Senior Product Marketing Manager        Software Project Manager      0.6071\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# ── Map each job title to closest candidate role ──\n",
        "# Note: this runs on 100k+ rows — sample for speed during dev\n",
        "# In production run on full dataset overnight\n",
        "\n",
        "def map_title_to_role(title):\n",
        "    if pd.isna(title) or str(title).strip() == '':\n",
        "        return 'Unknown', 0\n",
        "    result = process.extractOne(\n",
        "        str(title),\n",
        "        JOB_ROLES,\n",
        "        scorer=fuzz.token_sort_ratio\n",
        "    )\n",
        "    if result:\n",
        "        match, score, _ = result\n",
        "        return match, round(score / 100, 4)   # normalize to 0-1\n",
        "    return 'Unknown', 0\n",
        "\n",
        "# Run on a sample first to verify, then full dataset\n",
        "SAMPLE = job_df.head(5000).copy()\n",
